Israel told foreigners to evacuate ahead of "full occupation": Shaath 
A senior Palestinian official said here Saturday that the Israeli army
told foreign military attaches in Tel Aviv to evacuate their nationals
from ``lfstinian territories ahead of their "full occupation".
"We know from foreign military attaches in Tel Aviv that the Israeli
chief of staff informed them that the operation will lead to the
occupation of all the (Palestinian) towns and asked them to evacuate
all their nationals," international cooperation minister Nabil Shaath
said in Amman.
